snippet.title: Bahnsen Knights - Release Date Announce Trailer
snippet.description:
1986, Tornado Alley, USA… Go undercover as Boulder, an agent infiltrating the notorious religious cult known as the Bahnsen Knights. Face off against occultists, biblical storms, and an enigmatic car salesman turned preacher as you investigate the disappearance of a fellow agent and close friend in this dark interactive adventure.

Coming to Steam, PlayStation 4/5, Xbox and Nintendo Switch on 26th October 2023. 

Wishlist on Steam now: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1933190/Bahnsen_Knights/
